twitch_info.title: I Wanna Break the Series Z3 - Series Z2 Medley (Stage 4 Boss)
twitch_info.description: 3 hours. Surprisingly fun but not the greatest boss. P1 was fun, P2 was kinda eh and the hardest with the homing attack, P3 was mainly pattern with a tricky attack at the start and P4 was tough but thankfully only took a few attempts. Onto stage 5!
